WEBVTT

00:00:00.486 --> 00:00:03.455
Bugun men sizlarga mening eng

00:00:03.455 --> 00:00:04.812
sevimli mavzularimdan biri

00:00:04.812 --> 00:00:08.264
uyqu nevrologiyasi haqida gapiraman.

00:00:08.264 --> 00:00:11.348
Shunday bir sado bor--

00:00:11.348 --> 00:00:13.228
( budilnik qo'ng'irog'i)

00:00:13.228 --> 00:00:15.340
aah, ana tas'ir qildi --

00:00:15.340 --> 00:00:18.923
hammamizga juda yaxshi ma'lum bo'lgan shovqin bu,

00:00:18.923 --> 00:00:21.109
bu albatta budilnik ovozi.

00:00:21.109 --> 00:00:24.168
Va bu eng yoqimsiz sado,

00:00:24.168 --> 00:00:29.555
biz uchun eng muhim bo'lgan

00:00:29.555 --> 00:00:32.732
uyquni to'xtatadi.